{
	"digest": "Camera with special frustum control",
	"description" : {
        "desc1" : "Camera in 3D space with buildin lookat functionality. The node  will orient the camera in such a way, that the near-clip plane will lie on the lookat plane. To be used to create controlled cuts through objects or cave-like VR experiences",
        "desc2" : "LookAtCamera represents the virtual camera chassis, while SceneCapture represents the virtual film: For capturing the textures SceneCapture is needed."
	}
